  "commentary": "**DEALER HEDGING COMMENTARY:**\n\nSPX is currently trading 7.61 points above the GEX flip at 6776, putting us in positive gamma territory where dealers will sell rallies and buy dips. With spot at 6807.61 sitting between the massive +73B gamma wall at 6800 (where dealers are actively selling) and the +70B wall at 6810, we're in a high-density stabilization zone that should cap upward momentum. The wall_break event suggests we just pushed through resistance, but the thick gamma cushion from 6800-6825 (280B+ combined) will create significant headwinds for any sustained move higher.\n\nKey levels: watch 6800 as the primary dealer selling zone and 6776 GEX flip as the regime boundary - any break below flips dealers to short gamma and destabilizing behavior.\n\n**Bottom line:** expect price to get pinned and grind sideways between 6800-6810 as dealers lean against the move.",
